  "texts": [
    "We also fitted an RF classifier to predict COVID-19 status from self-reported symptoms and demographic data.",
    "The outcome used to train and test each of the prediction models was a participant's SARS-CoV-2 PCR test result.",
    "Each model's inputs and predictors, and the details on how they are handled, can be found below.",
    "Wherever applicable, we have reported our study's findings in accordance with TRIPOD statement guidelines 32.",
    "The following measures were used to assess model performance: ROC-AUC, area under the precision-recall curve (PR-AUC), and UAR (also known as balanced accuracy)."
  ],
